Enterprise Analytics & Demand Forecasting Dashboard

Power BI | PostgreSQL | SQL | Python | Scikit-Learn | Random Forest Regression

Overview

The Enterprise Analytics & Demand Forecasting Dashboard is an end-to-end Business Intelligence solution designed to provide actionable insights across Sales, Customer Analytics, Supply Chain Operations, and AI-powered Demand Forecasting.

The project combines data engineering, analytics, machine learning, and interactive visualization to help businesses monitor performance, identify trends, optimize operations, and make data-driven decisions.

