Database Design
Customers Table
Column	Description
Customer_ID	Unique Customer Identifier
Customer_Name	Customer Name
Segment	Customer Segment
Region	Business Region
Market	Market Classification
Products Table
Column	Description
Product_ID	Unique Product Identifier
Product_Name	Product Name
Category	Product Category
Sub_Category	Product Subcategory
Orders Table
Column	Description
Order_ID	Unique Order Identifier
Order_Date	Order Date
Ship_Date	Shipping Date
Sales	Sales Amount
Quantity	Quantity Sold
Discount	Discount Applied
Profit	Profit Earned
Shipping_Cost	Shipping Cost
Machine Learning Model
Random Forest Regression

A Random Forest Regression model was implemented to forecast future demand and revenue using historical sales data.

Why Random Forest?
Handles non-linear relationships effectively
Reduces overfitting through ensemble learning
High predictive accuracy
Works well on business datasets
Requires minimal feature engineering
Forecasting Workflow
Historical sales data collection
Data cleaning and preprocessing
Feature engineering
Model training using Random Forest Regression
Demand prediction
Revenue forecasting
Dashboard integration in Power BI
